== Overview ==
The Magma Cannon is a high pressure gas laser utilizing an explosive mixture of ultra heated oxidized gases normally found inside volcanic activity.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Magma Cannon can be bought in the workshop after obtaining [[Magma Technology]].
